{
  "stem": "7094.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they felt that my documents were very interesting, because they were not false documents.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, they were really creative.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were really created.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were real documents all along.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So-- and I was so eager to go back to being Henia Meller, that I said, yes, you can have it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now I regret it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I would have liked to have the documents.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I've searched for them in Yad Vashem.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Somebody told me-- and I couldn't find it there-- that maybe there is in Warsaw a-- a document-- a institute for Jewish history, that maybe I'll find there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Maybe one day I'll go to Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Maybe one day I'll write to get it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I would have liked to have the documents, just to prove to myself--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To those people, because they were collecting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I just wanted to go back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't want to have any part of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, well, if it's useful for you, have it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now I wish I would have kept it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there I stayed overnight with a Jewish family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I was trying to trace back, to go back to Sadowa Wisznia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Obviously Sadowa Wisznia-- I didn't realize that the borderline, between Poland and Russia was going through Przemysl, which is next to Sadowa Wisznia, is in Poland.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Sadowa Wisznia and Lwow is in the Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I had to go-- to cross the border.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And having this experience with Russians, I didn't want to see another Russian in my life.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I didn't want to go to Russia, because I was afraid that I won't come back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But in Przemysl I met two or three people who survived in Sadowa Wisznia all through the war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they told me that there is nobody there, nobody.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
